Weather Forecast Application

This is a simple weather forecast web application built using HTML, JavaScript, and Tailwind CSS.

Features:

Search weather by city name

Get weather for current location

Display current weather (temperature, humidity, wind, condition)

Show 5-day weather forecast

Recent searches using localStorage

Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop

Error handling and input validation

How to Use:

Open index.html in your browser.

Enter a city name and click Search or click üìç to get weather using your current location.

Recent searches appear in a dropdown for quick access.

Setup:

Replace 'YOUR_API_KEY' in the script section with your OpenWeatherMap API key.

Get your key from: https://openweathermap.org/api

Files

index.html: file with HTML, CSS (Tailwind), and 
main.js: file with JavaScript

